TextEng: Just wondering who you are.
You look like an adventurer.
I'll be going.
The competition? What's that?
Right, the competition. I don't think I'd want to risk it.
Text: 맞아요, 대회. 위험을 감수하고 싶진 않네요.

TextEng: I intend to enter the competition, myself, actually.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I might be up for a contest. Tell me about it.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 대회에 관심 있을 것 같아요. 말해주세요.

TextEng: How about 100 gold for you to tell me about it?
Ah. Well, I wouldn't be interested in such a thing, then.
Text: 아. 그럼 저는 그런 것에 관심 없네요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> My apologies. It's just something I'd be interested in trying.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 죄송합니다. 그냥 해보고 싶은 것 같아서요.

TextEng: Me just wonders what you name is.
Is you an adventurer like me is?
Me go now.
Me not know. What is competition?
Oh, right. Me knows that. Me not doing competition, though.
Text: 아, 맞아. 나 알아. 근데 나 대회 안 해.

TextEng: Me is entering competition!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me not know what contest is. You tell me now, okay?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 대회 뭔지 몰라. 지금 말해줘, 응?

TextEng: Me gives 100 gold if you tells me 'bout contest.
Me not care about such thing. No big deal is contest.
Text: 나 그런 거 관심 없어. 대회 별거 아니야.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me sorry. Me just think competition sound fun!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 미안. 나 그냥 대회 재밌을 것 같아서!

TextEng: Why me cares?
Me see what me can do. You holds on.
Text: 나 뭐 할 수 있는지 봐. 기다려.

TextEng: Yes, me can heals you.
Here... you takes healing potion.
You wants healing so you be in contest again.
Text: 너 치료받아서 다시 대회 하고 싶어.

TextEng: You be hurt? What hurt you?
Why should I care?
Tough. Me can handles myself.
Maybe me should ends your misery.
Tough. I can handle myself.
Text: 힘듭니다. 저 혼자 감당할 수 있어요.

TextEng: Perhaps I should put you out of your misery.
I'll see what I can do. Hold on.
Text: 뭘 할 수 있는지 볼게요. 기다리세요.

TextEng: Yes, I can heal you.
Here... take a healing potion.
You want me to heal you and put you back in the contest?
Text: 날 치료해서 다시 대회에 참가하게 해달라고요?

TextEng: You're injured? What did this to you?
You forget it. You enters contest, just likes me.
Text: 너 잊어. 너 대회 참가했어, 나처럼.

TextEng: Forget it. You entered the contest, just like me.
